wiki.summary: "Holiday" (stylized in all caps) is a song by American rapper Lil Nas X. It was released on November 13, 2020 through Columbia Records. A preview of the song, titled "The Origins of Holiday", was released on November 8. It is a Christmas-themed song, described as a stopgap single between his debut EP 7 and follow-up single "Montero (Call Me by Your Name)". Read more on Last.fm.
